<#c0a8f8>:Unique Trait:</>		"Asmos"
Lucy's staff weapon, Asmos, can be connected and
disconnected through her Craze Technique, which changes
how her moves function. _AC moves can only be used while
Asmos is connected, and _AD moves can only be used while
Asmos is disconnected.

